title: In-N-Out Burger Restaurant Locations 12.2007
name: In-N-Out Burger Restaurant Locations 12.2007
description:
In-N-Out Burger is a privately owned fast food restaurant chain in the western United States. The chain opened in 1948 and is headquartered in Irvine, California. In-N-Out Burger has locations in Arizona, California, and Nevada. The restaurant sells mainly burgers and fries and a few other items. They currently as of 12.2007 have 211 locations with others being constructed to be open in the future.

This dataset displays all of the In-N-Out Burger Restaurant locations across the United States. The dataset contains the store's full physical address, phone, and lat/lon coordinates. Addresses were obtained from in-n-out.com and are current as of 12.2007. Addresses were geocoded to obtain their lat/lon coordinates.

For more information, go to in-n-out.com

Data accessed on December 19, 2007
